Package: scholar
Maintainer: James Keirstead <j.keirstead@imperial.ac.uk>
Author: James Keirstead <j.keirstead@imperial.ac.uk>
Version: 0.1.0
License: Apache 2
Title: Analyse citation data from Google Scholar
Description: scholar provides functions to extract citation data from Google
    Scholar.  Convenience functions are also provided for comparing multiple
    scholars and predicting future h-index values.
Date: 2013-10-21
Depends:
    XML
Imports:
    stringr,
    plyr
Suggests:
    roxygen2
Collate:
    'scholar-package.r'
    'scholar.r'
    'predict.r'
    'compare.r'
    'publications.r'
